<h1>Privacy Statement</h1>
<article>
  <p>At Flourish, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Statement outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our web app.</p>

  <p><strong>1. Information We Collect</strong></p>
  <p>When you sign up for Flourish, we collect the following information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email Address: To verify your identity, send notifications, and provide newsletters.</li>
    <li>PayPal.Me Handle: To facilitate transactions as part of our app's functionality.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>2. How We Use Your Information</strong></p>
  <p>The information you provide is used for the following purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Account Management: Verifying your email address during registration and managing your account.</li>
    <li>Transactions: Using your PayPal.Me handle to enable secure payments or transfers as part of the app's features.</li>
    <li>Communication: Sending important updates, notifications, and newsletters about Flourish.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>3. Sharing Your Information</strong></p>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your data with trusted service providers to facilitate app functionality, such as:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email service providers for sending communications.</li>
    <li>Payment processors like PayPal for handling transactions.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>4. Data Security</strong></p>
  <p>We implement robust measures to safeguard your data, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Encryption for data transmission.</li>
    <li>Secure storage of sensitive information.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>5. Your Rights</strong></p>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
    <li>Opt-out of newsletters or notifications at any time via the unsubscribe link provided in our emails.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>6. Cookies and Tracking</strong></p>
  <p>Flourish may use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze site traffic. You can control cookie settings through your browser.</p>

  <p><strong>7. Updates to This Policy</strong></p>
  <p>This Privacy Statement may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices or services. Any significant changes will be communicated via email or the app.</p>

  <p><strong>8. Contact Us</strong></p>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy, please contact us at:</p>
  <p><i>Email</i>: <span data-controller="support" data-support-target="email"></span></p>
  <p>Your trust is important to us, and we are dedicated to ensuring your information is used responsibly and securely.</p>
</article>
